author: Billyfighter
description:
Several new additions to Starwind.

New items for sale at:
Taris Upper City Martet
Taris Lower City Blackmarket
old Nar Shaddaa overhauled district
Tatooine, Sandreach

name: Scientist
description: Scientists are masters at repairing and building almost anything, with some minimal training in combat.

name: Marauder
description: The Marauder is skilled in powerful combat and force abilities. They often work for themselves, destroying and stealing from their enemies with no remorse.

name: Juggernaut
description: The Juggernaut is skilled in heavy armor and combat with multiple different weapons. They're also proficient at constructing mechanical enhancements for their gear.

name: Assassin Droid
description: These type of droids are expert assassins. They're excellent at hunting down prey, but lack good communication skills. Assassin droids are usually known to be deceptive.

name: Devaronian
description: A sentient species from the planet Devaron. This race is said to be able to easily read and bend minds, many of whom are strong in the force.

name: Twi'lek (Red)
description: Native to Ryloth, the Twi'leks are very agile and sneaky. However they are not very persuasive and lack the Willpower to utulize it for anything worthwile.

name: Trandoshan
description: Large, bipedal reptilian humanoids from the planet Tradosha. They have the ability to generate lost limbs and eyes that can see in infrared range. They're known to periodically shed their skin.

Begin SWE_CzElevatorScr

float timer

if (MenuMode == 1)
	return
endif

set timer to ( timer + GetSecondsPassed )

if ( timer > 3 )
	if ( timer < 6 )
		MoveWorld z -180
	endif
endif

if ( timer > 9 )
	if ( timer < 12 )
		MoveWorld z 180
	endif
endif

if ( timer > 15 )
	SetAtStart
	set timer to 0
endif

if (CellChanged == 1)
	set timer to 0
	SetAtStart
endif

End

Begin SWE_SandReManorTerminal

short button
short messageOn

if ( SWE_SandReManorGlobal == 0 )
	if ( OnActivate == 1 )
		MessageBox "Would you like to purchase this hut for 2000 credits?" "Yes" "No"
		set messageOn to 1
	endif

	if ( messageOn == 1 )
		set button to GetButtonPressed

		if ( button >= 0 )
			set messageOn to 0
		endif

		if ( button == 0 )
            if ( player->GetItemCount "Gold_001" >= 2000 )
                MessageBox "You've successfully purchased the manor."
                player->RemoveItem "Gold_001" 2000
			PlaySound "Menu Click"
                Set SWE_SandReManorGlobal to 1
                return
            else
                MessageBox "You don't have enough credits for this manor."
			PlaySound "Menu Click"
                return
            endif
		elseif ( button == 1 )
			set button to 0
			return
		endif

	endif
endif

if ( SWE_SandReManorGlobal == 1 )

	if ( OnActivate == 1 )
		MessageBox "Control the door to your manor:" "Lock" "Unlock"
		set messageOn to 1
	endif

	if ( messageOn == 1 )
		set button to GetButtonPressed

		if ( button >= 0 )
			set messageOn to 0
		endif

		if ( button == 0 )
			MessageBox "Door locked."
			PlaySound "Menu Click"
			SWE_TatDoorSandReManOWN->Lock 50
			return
		elseif ( button == 1 )
			MessageBox "Door unlocked."
			PlaySound "Menu Click"
			SWE_TatDoorSandReManOWN->Unlock
			set button to 0
			return
		endif

	endif

endif

End

Begin SW_DoorBilly

If ( OnActivate )
	MessageBox "This door is jammed." "OK"
	Return
Endif

End

name: Coruscant
description: You grew up around many different people on your home planet of Coruscant, learning a diverse set of skills.

name: Endor
description: Your time on Endor gave you a naturally gifted immune system.

name: Felucia
description: You were born in a wild jungle enviornment, able to navigate difficult terrain.

name: Hoth
description: On a cold and remote planet, you were born to endure and live in harsh enviornments. Traveling anywhere else never seems to be a problem.

name: Lok
description: Scoundrels and smugglers have taught you a thing or two on how to get around in life.

name: Mandalore
description: You were born among warriors, trained in combat. No matter the weapon, you always have an edge.

name: Naboo
description: Born on the peaceful planet of Naboo, you grew up swimming among Gungans. You can deep dive and hold your breath underwater for long peroids.

name: Unknown
description: It's unknown where you were born. Though you've always been gifted with mysterious powers.

text: Stolen from Sandreach
Borg Reegh, a resident at Sandreach South Bay mentioned some stolen ship parts the sand people nearby took from him. If I find any stolen ship parts I should bring it to him.

Czerka Underground

Those sand people in Death Canyon I bet. They they took some crates which have stuff that belongs to my ship in em'. If you find any stolen ship parts bring em' here.
Yeah, those sand people in Death Canyon I bet. They they took some crates which have stuff that belongs to my ship in em'. If you find any stolen ship parts bring em' here.
